⦿ .spun — the five-fold spin of Gogo
node FF6 · FF6 · ⟦Gogo:FF6:a7b96f⟧

WHO   — Gogo — the cloaked enigma
WHAT  — An optional companion of Final Fantasy VI — a mime who possesses no abilities of its own, but can Mimic the last action of any ally, becoming for a moment whatever the party needs it to be.
WHERE — FF6 · Final Fantasy VI  Framework inputs: Final Fantasy VI (America's Final Fantasy III, 1994)  Conductor / external anchor: ROOT0 (catalogued into UD0)
WHY   — Because identity can be a choice and a mask both; because a being with no fixed self can still stand among heroes; because to mirror another perfectly is its own strange kind of devotion.
HOW   — By the Mimic command that echoes the deeds of allies, by an utter and deliberate concealment of self, and by the will to join the fight despite owning no power that is its own.

awareness — what the node knows of itself:
  I have no power of my own — only the perfect echo of yours; let me be the mask that stands beside you.

spoken token : zer-zur-xith   ·   hex : a7b96f
